    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later‚ at night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1300,
          "startTime": 1.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.1333333532
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……沙季ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Saki-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7666668455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん、どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan‚ what’s up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666668455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "えっとね、私は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3333335121,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2300.000119299999,
          "startTime": 9.6333336314
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　渚ちゃんに、沙季ちゃんも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Nagisa-chan and Saki-chan too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9000010053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなしてどうしたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s going on with everyone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2000010053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストで話し合う時、この時間帯にリビングで集まる\nことが多かったでしょ？　その時のクセでつい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we had discussions as Moon Tempest‚ we often gathered in the living room\naround this time‚ right? I guess it’s just a habit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7432421246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣もそんな感じだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei did too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7333343386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "私も同じようなものですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Same here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9666676719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "習慣はすぐには抜けないものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess habits die hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3666676719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、みんな。ちょっとだけお話ししない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ everyone. Want to talk for a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0333343188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 43.0666699607
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、お茶を淹れました。カフェインの入っていない\nルイボスティーですから、安心して飲んで下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I made some tea. It’s caffeine-free\nrooibos tea‚ so you can drink it without worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8666699409,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6366.6633924,
          "startTime": 54.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃん、ありがとう\n……うん、美味しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Saki-chan.\n…Mmm‚ delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7000032742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなはお休みの間、どうしてたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did everyone do during their time off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.0333366274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私は食べ歩きをしたり、マンガを読んだり……\n久しぶりの連休を謳歌させてもらいましたわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I went around eating good food‚ read some manga…\nI enjoyed my long-awaited holidays!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2666699409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　でもすずにゃん、しょっちゅう\n月をぼーっと見てなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But Suzu-nyan‚ weren’t you\nstaring blankly at the moon all the time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3666699409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "し、自然を愛でていたんですのよ！\nアイドルたるもの、いつ何時でも感性を磨きませんと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I was appreciating nature!\nAs an idol‚ you have to constantly refine your sensibilities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3000032742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "私は千紗が時間を作ってくれたので\n久しぶりに姉妹水入らずで過ごせました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa made time for me‚ so we were able to spend\nsome quality time as sisters for the first time in a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4000032742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。私もあちこちに出かけてたんだけど……\nやっぱり、どこにいても月ストのことを考えちゃってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I went out to various places‚ but…\nI kept thinking about Moon Tempest wherever I went.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6666699409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 98.1666684348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "それは……私もですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s… me too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1666684348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "このお店で打ち上げをしたなーとか\nここを五人で走ったなーとか、いくらでも思い出すよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ “We had our after-party at this place‚” or\n“We ran through here as five.” There are so many things to remember.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.566668415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "私も……五人で頑張ってきた記憶が\nいろんな場所に染み付いているんだなって気付きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized… that our memories of working hard together as five\nare embedded in so many places.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9000017483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "……私ね、琴乃ちゃんが脱退する前に\n琴乃ちゃん本人から話を聞いてたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You know‚ before Kotono-chan left‚\nI heard from her directly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2666668891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2000002423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "うん。それで、琴乃ちゃんに\n一緒に来ないかって、誘われて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. And she asked me\nif I wanted to come with her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5666668891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "大変！　それじゃ月ストが三人になっちゃう……\nって、あれ？　でも、渚ちゃんが残ったってことは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no! Then Moon Tempest would be down to three members…\nWait‚ huh? But if Nagisa-chan stayed‚ that means…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7000002224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 148.2666638571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、私は月ストに残るよって言ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I told her I’m staying with Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.2666638571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、ごめんね？\nこんな大事なこと、今まで黙ってて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry‚ everyone.\nI’m sorry for keeping quiet about such an important matter…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.233330504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことが……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That happened…?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.6666638571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめん、話すタイミングがなかったんだ\nそれに、琴乃ちゃんもきっと心細くて私を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry‚ I just didn’t have a chance to tell you.\nBesides‚ Kotono-chan must have been feeling uneasy and she——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1552716483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんが琴乃ちゃんの誘いを断るなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You turned down Kotono-chan’s invitation…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9333335755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "え、そっちの驚き？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ is that what you’re surprised about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.4000002422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、芽衣もびっくりした。だって渚ちゃん\n本当に琴乃ちゃんのこと大好きだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I was surprised too. Because you\nreally love Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.7999920843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわよ。琴乃が渚を誘う気持ちも分かりますし\n何より……よく琴乃をフりましたわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. I understand why Kotono would ask you‚\nbut more importantly… You rejected her?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.7479986546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "フ、フるとか、そんなんじゃないから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Reject is… it wasn’t like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.0666719951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "……でもね、その時は\n琴乃ちゃんがいつかは戻って来るって思ってたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But you see‚ at that time‚\nI thought Kotono-chan would come back someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.666658751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "だから、これからどうするか……ずっと悩んでた\nもちろん、みんなも同じだと思うけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I’ve been wondering what to do…\nI’m sure you all feel the same way‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.5999920843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "そう、ですね。私も随分と考えました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’ve been thinking a lot about it too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.7333386617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 216.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達も一杯考えてたけどさ\n{user}さんのあんな顔、初めて見たよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve been thinking a lot too‚\nbut that was the first time I saw {user}-san make a face like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.1333254176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
