      "text": "言われてみれば……そうですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it… that’s true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.6000053284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがあんな切羽詰まった顔を\nするなんて……よほどのこと、なんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For {user}-san to make such a desperate face…\nThis must be a really big deal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.266658751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "私達月ストの歩んできた道のりの中でも……\nおそらく、今が最大の正念場ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the history of Moon Tempest…\nthis is probably our biggest turning point.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.61050985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、みんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.8666719951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "四人で月ストを続けるか、それとも解散するか……\nせーので言ってみない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether we continue Moon Tempest as four‚ or disband…\nwhy don’t we say it on the count of three?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.7999920843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "いいと思います。やってみましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think that’s a good idea. Let’s do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.8333366272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_06_04-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "同時に言ったらごちゃごちゃになりませんの？\nでも、まぁ……",
      "translations": {
